# Local state lives only in this directory by design (chicken-and-egg);
# never commit it.
.local-state/
terraform.tfstate
terraform.tfstate.backup
.terraform/
# `.terraform.lock.hcl` IS committed for this workspace too (per ADR-0018
# + rule 81). CI does not run init against this workspace (it has local
# state) but committing the lock keeps the provider set transparent.
tfplan
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
